flowchart TD
    A[/setup GET] --> B{Any admin exists?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Redirect to /login]
    B -->|No| D[Render admin bootstrap form]
    D --> E[/setup POST]
    E --> F[Validate CSRF]
    F --> G[Validate email + password]
    G --> H{Email available?}
    H -->|No| I[Show error]
    H -->|Yes| J[Create user with is_admin = 1]
    J --> K[Hash password with PASSWORD_DEFAULT]
    K --> L[Redirect to /login with success message]
